1059
00:38:45,903 --> 00:38:47,872
Right. Yes. Hi.

1060
00:38:47,873 --> 00:38:50,043
Yes. Let's speak casually at once.

1061
00:38:50,283 --> 00:38:51,342
Yes.

1062
00:38:51,343 --> 00:38:53,082
