1078
00:39:25,443 --> 00:39:27,583
I won't be able to have durian snacks.

1079
00:39:27,813 --> 00:39:28,983
Gosh. I won't.

1080
00:39:29,983 --> 00:39:32,422
Why am I worried?

1081
00:39:32,423 --> 00:39:33,669
(As they don't know about the work, they're even more worried.)

1082
00:39:33,693 --> 00:39:36,322
