1085
00:39:40,093 --> 00:39:41,992
I'm so worried, Jun Myun.

1086
00:39:41,993 --> 00:39:43,432
Did you get some sleep?

1087
00:39:43,433 --> 00:39:44,903
I couldn't sleep.

1088
00:39:45,533 --> 00:39:47,532
