1095
00:40:00,883 --> 00:40:02,913
I think she's coming.

1096
00:40:03,253 --> 00:40:05,383
She's in vacation mode.

1097
00:40:05,883 --> 00:40:07,023
- Yes. - She looks...

1098
00:40:07,693 --> 00:40:09,252
(From the trench coat...)

1099
00:40:09,253 --> 00:40:11,093
(to the sunglasses, )

1100
00:40:11,823 --> 00:40:14,793
