1104
00:40:19,434 --> 00:40:20,573
- Hello. - Gosh.

1105
00:40:20,773 --> 00:40:22,972
- Hello. - Hi.

1106
00:40:22,973 --> 00:40:24,873
- It's so heavy. - That must've been tough.

1107
