1128
00:41:01,973 --> 00:41:04,182
It says Bohol right here.

1129
00:41:04,183 --> 00:41:05,583
- Is it Bohol? - Bohol.

1130
00:41:05,683 --> 00:41:07,283
- Bohol, the Philippines. - Bohol?

1131
00:41:07,553 --> 00:41:09,113
- Is Bohol in the Philippines? - Bohol.

1132
00:41:14,193 --> 00:41:17,293
(The Philippines)

1133
00:41:20,493 --> 00:41:23,293
(Bohol)

1134
00:41:25,663 --> 00:41:29,273
