1148
00:42:11,983 --> 00:42:14,413
(Nothing. Enjoy.)

1149
00:42:20,893 --> 00:42:22,253
Hye Yoon is good.

1150
00:42:22,453 --> 00:42:24,092
This is a vacation, indeed.

1151
00:42:24,093 --> 00:42:27,993
(The siblings' summer story)

1152
00:42:28,793 --> 00:42:32,033
