1165
00:43:04,863 --> 00:43:06,232
I couldn't find you.

1166
00:43:06,233 --> 00:43:08,773
- I went, "Where are they?" - I didn't recognize you.

1167
00:43:08,903 --> 00:43:10,602
- It was the Philippines, indeed. - Nice to see you.

1168
00:43:10,603 --> 00:43:11,843
- Exactly. - Let's go that way.

1169
00:43:12,373 --> 00:43:14,842
- Gosh. It's summer, indeed. - Right?

1170
00:43:14,843 --> 00:43:15,873
It's hot.

1171
00:43:16,073 --> 00:43:17,312
