1172
00:43:17,313 --> 00:43:19,512
- Because it's nighttime, - Exactly.

1173
00:43:19,513 --> 00:43:20,583
It's a bit windy.

1174
00:43:21,083 --> 00:43:24,552
Okay. Welcome to Bohol, Philippines.

1175
00:43:24,553 --> 00:43:26,252
