- We'll go to the hotel first. - Okay.

1177
00:43:28,523 --> 00:43:29,822
- On your schedule, - Yes.

1178
00:43:29,823 --> 00:43:31,922
What was your first activity?

1179
00:43:31,923 --> 00:43:33,833
- Labor. - It was labor.

1180
00:43:34,033 --> 00:43:36,693
So, take a good rest. And tomorrow,

1181
00:43:36,963 --> 00:43:39,763
we'll gather at 6am in the lobby.

1182
00:43:40,119 --> 00:43:42,719
So, take a good rest. And tomorrow,

1183
00:43:43,049 --> 00:43:45,859
we'll gather at 6am in the lobby.

1184
00:43:45,989 --> 00:43:47,118
- Did you say 6am? - Yes.

1185
00:43:47,119 --> 00:43:50,029
(The early call time removes light from their faces.)

1186
00:43:50,189 --> 00:43:53,258
(There's no plane to escape.)

1187
00:43:53,259 --> 00:43:54,899
It's okay. I can just wake up at 5am.

1188
00:43:55,999 --> 00:43:58,038
Why do I feel like we'll go to the jungle?

1189
00:43:58,039 --> 00:43:59,398
- Jungle? - Into the wilderness.

1190
00:43:59,399 --> 00:44:00,539
Did you say the jungle?

1191
00:44:00,839 --> 00:44:02,668
- Let's think about it tomorrow. - Think about it tomorrow.

1192
00:44:02,669 --> 00:44:04,038
Let's focus on today for now.

1193
00:44:04,039 --> 00:44:06,119
(What will be their first labor in the Philippines?)

1194
00:44:07,409 --> 00:44:09,979
