1199
00:44:27,569 --> 00:44:28,999
Gosh. It's crazy.

1200
00:44:30,029 --> 00:44:31,038
- Goodness. - Hello.

1201
00:44:31,039 --> 00:44:32,738
(Dex and Jun Myun are the first ones to arrive.)

1202
00:44:32,739 --> 00:44:35,139
- What's with your hand in the end? - This place is awesome.

1203
00:44:35,639 --> 00:44:37,609
So beautiful.

1204
00:44:39,209 --> 00:44:40,748
(You can see the blue ocean...)

1205
00:44:40,749 --> 00:44:43,049
(over the hotel.)

1206
00:44:43,509 --> 00:44:46,719
(In Bohol, you can see the beautiful ocean from anywhere.)

1207
00:44:47,919 --> 00:44:50,518
(She can't help but be amazed at the exotic view.)

1208
00:44:50,519 --> 00:44:52,958
- It's a nice pool. - All I can think about is work.

1209
00:44:52,959 --> 00:44:54,879
(But work is the only thing on Jun Myun's mind.)

1210
00:44:54,929 --> 00:44:57,629
(What will be their first labor in the Philippines?)

1211
00:44:57,959 --> 00:45:00,229
- The water comes up to the knees. - Gosh.

1212
00:45:00,499 --> 00:45:01,499
What?

1213
00:45:01,529 --> 00:45:03,028
The water is very shallow over here.

1214
00:45:03,029 --> 00:45:04,898
It only comes up to the knees when you see them.

1215
00:45:04,899 --> 00:45:06,998
Really? You're right.

1216
00:45:06,999 --> 00:45:09,869
