1224
00:45:25,089 --> 00:45:27,728
- Gosh. Hello. - Hey, Hye Yoon.

1225
00:45:27,729 --> 00:45:28,729
Hello.

1226
00:45:28,730 --> 00:45:30,189
- No need to run. - Hello.

1227
00:45:30,459 --> 00:45:32,858
- Hello, Jung Ah. - Hello.

1228
00:45:32,859 --> 00:45:34,669
- Hello. - Hi.

1229
00:45:34,729 --> 00:45:37,068
