1232
00:45:42,739 --> 00:45:44,578
- The envelope is full. - What's that?

1233
00:45:44,579 --> 00:45:45,909
Gosh. Jung Ah.

1234
00:45:46,509 --> 00:45:47,509
- Gosh. - Nice.

1235
00:45:48,279 --> 00:45:50,778
I don't know the currency exchange rate here.

1236
00:45:50,779 --> 00:45:53,649
What currency do they use here? Pesos?

1237
00:45:54,349 --> 00:45:55,449
(Surprised)

1238
00:45:55,549 --> 00:45:57,389
We've already decided who'd be the treasurer.

1239
