1242
00:46:06,599 --> 00:46:09,929
She's so capable, so we had to make her the treasurer.

1243
00:46:10,629 --> 00:46:12,898
She played a bank clerk in a movie.

1244
00:46:12,899 --> 00:46:14,138
Yes, she played a bank clerk,

1245
00:46:14,139 --> 00:46:15,768
