1246
00:46:15,769 --> 00:46:17,778
- Should I show it to you? - Gosh. Look.

1247
00:46:17,779 --> 00:46:19,008
She does have the skill.

1248
00:46:19,009 --> 00:46:20,879
- But the money is... - They're so soft.

1249
00:46:21,179 --> 00:46:22,448
Let's dry them, they're crisp.

1250
00:46:22,449 --> 00:46:24,849
She's different because she's a former bank clerk.

1251
00:46:26,619 --> 00:46:27,688
(Shall we go and work now?)

1252
00:46:27,689 --> 00:46:29,689
- Yes. - Yes. Let's go.

1253
00:46:29,789 --> 00:46:30,919
Let's go.

1254
00:46:31,489 --> 00:46:32,519
Let's go.

1255
