1256
00:46:35,929 --> 00:46:37,029
Hello.

1257
00:46:37,459 --> 00:46:39,999
Hello. Good morning.

1258
00:46:40,899 --> 00:46:42,368
Hello.

1259
00:46:42,369 --> 00:46:44,668
- Hello. - "Assigned Marker." Thank you.

1260
00:46:44,669 --> 00:46:46,389
- Hello. Good morning. - "Assigned Marker."

1261
00:46:46,439 --> 00:46:48,538
- Nice to meet you. - Nice to meet you.

1262
00:46:48,539 --> 00:46:50,338
- What's your name? - I'm Mark.

1263
00:46:50,339 --> 00:46:52,439
Mark. You're Assigned Marker.

1264
00:46:52,579 --> 00:46:53,778
(Mark: A local Filipino)

1265
00:46:53,779 --> 00:46:54,848
(A guide and driver who'll accompany the siblings for 5 days)

1266
00:46:54,849 --> 00:46:56,108
(Multi-lingual, fluent in Korean)

1267
00:46:56,109 --> 00:46:57,278
(Assigned Marker)

1268
00:46:57,279 --> 00:46:58,978
- Assigned Marker? - Yes.

1269
00:46:58,979 --> 00:47:00,255
(He'll be marking the siblings.)

1270
00:47:00,279 --> 00:47:01,618
- That's why he's Mark. - That's why.

1271
00:47:01,619 --> 00:47:03,059
- Okay. Let's go. - Assigned Marker.

1272
00:47:04,719 --> 00:47:06,659
Gosh. This car is nice. What is this?

1273
00:47:07,659 --> 00:47:09,788
Okay. We have to fasten our seatbelts.

1274
00:47:09,789 --> 00:47:11,629
(You have to wear seatbelts before you leave.)

1275
00:47:11,959 --> 00:47:15,699
(Now, let's leave for work.)

1276
00:47:15,929 --> 00:47:18,238
Mark, how long will it take?

1277
00:47:18,239 --> 00:47:20,869
Maybe an hour?

1278
00:47:20,969 --> 00:47:22,638
- An hour? - An hour?

1279
00:47:22,639 --> 00:47:23,968
About 50 minutes or an hour.

1280
00:47:23,969 --> 00:47:25,379
Gosh. It's far.

1281
00:47:25,739 --> 00:47:27,138
It takes about an hour to get there.

1282
00:47:27,139 --> 00:47:28,749
- Yes. - That's why we're leaving early.

1283
00:47:28,849 --> 00:47:31,279
Gosh. Look at the car they're riding. It's so cute.

1284
00:47:32,819 --> 00:47:36,149
